projectPostList.progress: It's a forum with the main page similar to 4chan kindaish and threads similar to reddit but with streamed comments.  Free tier expired so gonna take it down probably within a month. Everything gets auto purged every few days anyway. Mostly half works. Comments can be made anonymously but need to create an account to post articles/create collections of tags.
